    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">These ASR Tactical Boot Laces made with 950lb Technora cord are perfect for high-stress environments, such as outdoor survival, camping, work sites, hiking, and much more. These Technora cord laces can be used as an emergency supply of Technora to use in many different ways including securing tents to making a rescue line. The heavy duty aglets prevent splits in the shoelace and will make the lace last much longer than your average shoelace. The lace sizes measure 36&quot;, 48&quot;, 60&quot;, 72&quot;, 84&quot;, 96&quot; and 108&quot; long and will be perfect for any boots or shoes. Make sure to grab your Technora boot lace before you get caught in an emergency situation</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Tactical TitanLace 950 Technora Work Boot Lace (Multiple Sizes and Colors)</h2>\n  <p>These ASR Tactical Boot Laces made with 950lb Technora cord are perfect for high-stress environments, such as outdoor survival, camping, work sites, hiking, and much more.</p>\n  <p>These Technora cord laces can be used as an emergency supply of Technora to use in many different ways including securing tents to making a rescue line. The heavy duty aglets prevent splits in the shoelace and will make the lace last much longer than your average shoelace.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>UNIVERSAL FIT:</strong> Ideal replacement emergency cord laces for hiking boots and duty boots with 4mm metal aglet; Available Lengths: 36&quot;, 48&quot;, 60&quot;, 72&quot;, 84&quot;, 96&quot;, 108&quot;</li>\n    <li>Includes (1) Pair of Universal Upgrade Technora Laces for Standard Shoe Laces and Utility Boot Laces</li>\n    <li><strong>Breaking Strength:</strong> 950lbs with PTFE Protective Coating</li>\n    <li>Ideal for Work Boots, Backpacking, Camping, Outdoors, Hunting and Everyday Use</li>\n    <li>Made in the USA</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/Btnr030_main.jpg\" alt=\"These ASR Tactical Boot Laces made with 950lb Technora cord are perfect for high-stress environments, such as outdoor survival, camping, work sites\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> NORALACE3FT</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 766359999746</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The lace sizes measure 36&quot;, 48&quot;, 60&quot;, 72&quot;, 84&quot;, 96&quot; and 108&quot; long and will be perfect for any boots or shoes. Make sure to grab your Technora boot lace before you get caught in an emergency situation.</p>\n  <p>Shoelace Lengths: 36&quot; - 92cm - 4-5 Eyelets 48&quot; - 122cm - 6-7 Eyelets 60&quot; - 153cm - 7-8 Eyelets 72&quot; - 183cm - 8-9 Eyelets 84&quot; - 213cm - 9-10 Eyelets 96&quot; - 244cm - 10-11 Eyelets 108&quot; - 274cm - 11-12 Eyelets</p>\n  <p>Disclaimer: Shoelace aglet is 4mm in diameter, make sure your eyelets are the correct size before ordering.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "These ASR Tactical Boot Laces made with 950lb Technora cord are perfect for high-stress environments, such as outdoor survival, camping, work sites, hiking, and much more. These Technora cord laces can be used as an emergency supply of Technora to use in many different ways including securing tents to making a rescue line. The heavy duty aglets prevent splits in the shoelace and will make the lace last much longer than your average shoelace. The lace sizes measure 36\", 48\", 60\", 72\", 84\", 96\" and 108\" long and will be perfect for any boots or shoes. Make sure to grab your Technora boot lace before you get caught in an emergency situation.",
